Generous sized en suite upstairs so bring your king bed and oversized bedroom suit. Open kitchen/dining room makes for easy entertaining. Step out back to your oasis of privacy! Just minutes to I-264, Tide light rail transit, town center, and Sentara Leigh Hospital.  https://view.spiro.media/173_cheyenne_rd-6884?branding=false
